org.apache.metamodel.spring
Interface DataContextFactoryParameters

All Known Implementing Classes:
DataContextFactoryBean
public interface DataContextFactoryParameters

Represents parameters used by a factory DataContext objects. All getters in this interface may return null, since the parameters may be originating from an external configuration file or similar means.
